{\b\fs28 Vedion Screen Share — License & Disclosure}\par\par

{\b SCREEN CAPTURE DISCLOSURE}\par
This application captures your screen when you trigger it using a hotkey or interval you configure. 
Captured frames are sent only to destinations you explicitly set up: Discord webhooks and AI providers 
you supply API keys for. No data is transmitted automatically or without your action.\par\par

{\b WHAT THIS SOFTWARE DOES}\par
\bullet\tab Captures your screen (full or a region you select) on demand\par
\bullet\tab Sends screenshots to Discord webhooks you provide\par
\bullet\tab Sends screenshots to AI providers (Gemini, OpenAI, Claude, Groq, Ollama, or custom) using API keys you supply\par
\bullet\tab Runs silently in the system tray\par
\bullet\tab Stores your settings locally in %AppData%\\VedionScreenShare\\\par\par

{\b WHAT THIS SOFTWARE DOES NOT DO}\par
\bullet\tab Does not run continuously or capture in the background without your trigger\par
\bullet\tab Does not store screenshots on any Vedion server\par
\bullet\tab Does not transmit your API keys anywhere except the provider endpoint you configured\par
\bullet\tab Does not record audio, keystrokes, clipboard, or any data other than screen frames\par\par

{\b LICENSE}\par
This software is licensed, not sold. Your license key is valid for up to 2 machines at a time. 
You may transfer to a different machine up to 2 times per calendar month via your vedion.cloud account dashboard.\par\par

